column2: "Progress? I've made a little, but it's still going slowly."
"They've started to show their faces to me, but I still haven't been able to close the distance."
"I don't want to rush things and scare them off..."
"But it's disheartening that I can't get any closer than this."
"If you get too close, they're just going to run away... what?"
"Okay, I see. They weren't scared of me, I was just scared of failing."
